行公园（支持 Linkin Park）</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">《建筑师》杂志向我们介绍了《Whiplash》和新专辑《The Sky, The Earth &amp; All Between》：“如果我们现在不打算发挥我们的潜力，那我们什么时候才能实现呢？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 “爱和鼓励”爱莉安娜·格兰德说服杨紫琼扮演“邪恶”角色https://www.nme.com/news/film/loving-and-encouraging-ariana-grande-convinced-michelle-yeoh-to-take-wicked-role-3814117?ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=热爱并鼓励阿丽安娜·格兰德确信米歇尔·杨扮演邪恶的角色Damian JonesTue, 19 Nov 2024 17:31:08 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3814117 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杨紫琼和爱莉安娜·格兰德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位《一切都同时发生》的明星此前曾与导演乔恩·朱 (Jon M. Chu) 合作拍摄过《摘金奇缘》</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/loving-and-encouraging-ariana-grande-convinced-michelle-yeoh-to-take-wicked-role-3814117">“爱和鼓励”Ariana Grande 说服杨紫琼扮演“Wicked”角色</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="杨紫琼和爱莉安娜·格兰德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_michelleyeoh_arianagrande_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michelle-yeoh">杨紫琼</a>称赞<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德</a>和辛西娅·埃里沃说服她出演<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked">《魔法坏女巫》</a></em>中的角色。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/everything-everywhere-all-at-once-ending-explained-netflix-3591920">“一切同时无处不在”结局解释：伊芙琳回到了她自己的宇宙吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p>在电影中饰演魔法老师莫里布尔夫人的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/everything-everywhere-all-at-once"><i>《一切都在同时》的</i></a>女主角因不会唱歌而不愿出演这个角色。</p><p>乔恩·朱 (Jon M. Chu) 执导了 2018 年浪漫喜剧《摘金奇缘》 <i>(Crazy Rich Asians)</i>中的杨紫琼，当他邀请她加入时，她告诉<i><a href="https://www.thetimes.com/life-style/celebrity/article/michelle-yeoh-wicked-everything-everywhere-interview-mm338q739" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《泰晤士报》</a> ：</i> “我读了剧本并说，‘乔恩，你知道我不会唱歌。’”</p><p>她继续说道：“我收到的下一件事是与乔恩、阿丽亚娜和辛西娅的视频通话，他们三个人说，‘你现在必须来加入我们！’” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="邪恶女巫 - 官方预告片 2" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pqi45Qhq3CI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>杨从未看过原版舞台音乐剧，但最终同意这个角色并开始与埃里沃表演二重唱。</p><p> “他们非常有爱心和鼓励，”杨谈到三人组的投入时说道。 “他们为我找到了一位出色的声乐教练。辛西娅说，‘别害羞，你能做到的。’”</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/wicked-first-screening-has-rave-reviews-what-a-fantastic-movie-the-ultimate-crowd-pleaser-of-2024-3814030">《<em>魔法坏女巫</em>》昨晚（11 月 18 日）在伦敦举行了欧洲首映，反响非常积极</a>。</p><p>当首都南岸转变为翡翠城时，杨紫琼、格兰德、辛西娅和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-goldblum">杰夫·高布伦</a>等演员勇敢地面对雨天。</p><p>该电影改编自舞台音乐剧，讲述了<em>《绿野仙踪》中西方邪恶女巫的起源故事，</em>将于本周五（11 月 22 日）在英国和美国上映。</p><p>继《巴本海默》在 2023 年夏天席卷全球之后，影迷们正在期待本周晚些时候<em>《魔法坏女巫》</em>在美国对阵<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-ii"><em>《角斗士 2》</em></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/glicked-film-fans-prepare-for-gladiator-ii-and-wicked-release-day-doubleheader-3773336">的“Glicked”现象</a>。</p><p>这两部电影将在未来几天同时上映，就像去年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>一样，它们将在未来几天内<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/glicked-is-looking-to-rival-barbenheimer-for-box-office-success-3812040">掀起票房风暴</a>。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://deadline.com/2024/10/wicked-gladiator-ii-box-office-opening-1236163352/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deadline</a>报道，</em>乔恩·M·楚 (Jon M. Chu) 执导的《魔法坏女巫》 <em>(Wicked)</em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特 (Ridley Scott</a> ) 执导的<em>《角斗士 2》</em>首映票房收入预计将超过 8000 万美元（6280 万英镑），后者预计将获得 6500 万美元（5100 万英镑）的票房收入。国内。</p><p> <em>《魔法坏女巫》</em>预计也会受到女性的欢迎，而<em>《角斗士 2》</em>则将吸引男性和老年女性。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/loving-and-encouraging-ariana-grande-convinced-michelle-yeoh-to-take-wicked-role-3814117">“爱和鼓励”Ariana Grande 说服杨紫琼扮演“Wicked”角色</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
